comment_data.body:
Now I am thinking whether we should add here `if HAS_CYTHON` condition something like:
```python
if HAS_CYTHON:
    if build_in_temp:
        args = [quiet, "build_ext", '--c-build-dir', pyxbuild_dir]
    else:
        args = [quiet, "build_ext", '--c-build-dir', None]
else:
    args = [quiet, "build_ext"]
```

But I am not 100% sure when it is possible to have `HAS_CYTHON=False` (or in other words to have not cython present)
